description: GMA2000 provides an overall result for Year A Graduate entry Bachelor of Medical Science and Doctor of Medicine (MD) based upon achievement in GMA1010 and includes the Vertically Integrated Assessment (VIA) examination undertaken at the end of Year A. Teaching and learning activities for GMA1010 have been outlined in the relevant unit approvals and student results for each of these units will contribute to the result for GMA2000.
faculty: Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences
